I have to do that

293
00:24:51,520 --> 00:24:52,960
even if it’s hard.

294
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,000
My life

295
00:24:58,240 --> 00:25:00,080
is worth it.

296
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:47,760
Even the person you trust

297
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,960
will betray you.

298
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,560
Lu Ping.

299
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:54,960
I’ve said that you have nowhere to go.

300
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,800
Are you okay?

301
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,200
Is that hurt?

302
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,200
It has been long.

303
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:11,440
You’re the only one who dares to talk to me.

304
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:14,200
I am scared by my own.

305
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:17,520
I am not afraid when I am with you.

306
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:21,080
I am Su Tang. What’s your name?

307
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:22,600
I don’t know.

308
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:25,240
Since I am brought here,

309
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,260
they just have been torturing me.

310
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:29,760
I don’t remember my name.

311
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:33,280
Everyone has his name.

312
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,400
Lu Ping.

313
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:40,880
Call me Lu Ping.

314
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,000
I wish my future

315
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:45,000
can be smooth.

316
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,080
Su Tang.

317
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,000
Mo Lin.

318
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,240
Qin Sang.

319
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,760
Xifan.

320
00:27:23,320 --> 00:27:25,560
You are going to meet your disciple.

321
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:30,080
You want to

322
00:27:30,840 --> 00:27:32,520
torture him till now.

323
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,720
He should revenge for his father

324
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,560
by himself.

325
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:41,600
Song.

326
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:45,290
He is the son of our eldest brother and sister.

327
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,360
The only son.

328
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:50,040
You saw him born.

329
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,040
Haven’t you done enough to him?

330
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,200
Liu Song.

331
00:28:11,160 --> 00:28:12,080
Song.

332
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,760
I beg you.

333
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:20,480
Chu Min, the master of Yaoguang Peak.
Aren’t you fearless?

334
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,920
Why are you begging…

335
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,520
Shut up.

336
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,240
Guo Youdao is a fool.

337
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,440
You are weak.

338
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,770
He is the son of our eldest brother.

339
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,840
He needs to know the truth.

340
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,760
The truth you and Guo Youdao

341
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,120
dare not to find out.

342
00:29:21,020 --> 00:29:23,780
[Memorial Tablet for Eldest Brother Leng Xiutan]

343
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:38,220
You were half a year old when you left Big Dipper.

344
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,960
You are 19 years old now.

345
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:48,680
The incense is for you.

346
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:52,240
You don’t have to pretend here.

347
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:56,040
My parents wouldn’t have died

348
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:59,490
if you hadn’t brought the Shanhai Gang in.

349
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,940
I brought the Shanhai Gang in?

350
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:04,080
That’s what Yan Qiuci told you.

351
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,460
Why do you want to take revenge on him?

352
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:09,680
You spent three years in Zhaifeng.

353
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:12,600
You’ve learnt nothing from Guo Youdao.

354
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,850
What are you talking about?

355
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:19,160
No one tells you the truth.

356
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,120
I will.

357
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:23,840
I can’t find your parents’ bodies

358
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:26,920
in the fire of Qisha Institute.

359
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:30,320
I took you out.

360
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,640
We were both victims.

361
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:41,800
Who are you?

362
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:44,240
I am the prince of Dan.

363
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,960
My father sent me to Big Dipper in that year.

364
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:51,620
He hoped me to draw the forces of Jianghu,

365
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,920
and persuade Big Dipper to help Dan.

366
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,840
After I went to Big Dipper,

367
00:30:57,800 --> 00:31:00,760
I found that it was a paradise beyond the world.

368
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:04,800
Eldest brother treated me well.

369
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:08,080
Chu Min and I loved each other.

370
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:11,720
There was no infighting like in the palace,

371
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:14,440
only mutual support from the brothers.

372
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:20,320
Your father was obsessed with the martial arts.

373
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:23,100
He never wanted to involve politics.

374
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:24,560
I was in dilemma.

375
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:28,060
I didn’t know whether I should tell the truth

376
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,400
to eldest brother.

377
00:31:29,940 --> 00:31:33,820
[Memorial Tablet for Eldest Brother Leng Xiutan]

378
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,480
Until you, the awakening who can use six forces,

379
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:40,080
were born.

380
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,920
My father knew that.

381
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:45,530
He thought you were the key
to enhancing the power of Dan.

382
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:48,240
He told me to take you away.

383
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:59,140
[Big Dipper Institute]

384
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,480
Song.

385
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,800
Why did you steal Ping’er?

386
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:33,560
What do you want?

387
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:46,340
It’s the commander’s seal of Dan.

388
00:32:47,520 --> 00:32:48,120
Speak.

389
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:50,280
Who are you?

390
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:53,920
Dan is in danger.

391
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:55,680
I am the prince of Dan.

392
00:32:56,280 --> 00:32:58,360
I need to seek interests for my country.

393
00:32:58,360 --> 00:33:00,960
You ignored the life of a half-year-old child.

394
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,850
How can you talk about the justice?

395
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:06,640
Today,

396
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,720
I got caught by you.

397
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,680
I have nothing to say.

398
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:13,400
Please do anything

399
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,160
as you like.

400
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:18,200
I can forgive you.

401
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:24,160
But Big Dipper never interferes into politics.

402
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,400
You have two ways to go.

403
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:28,680
Firstly,

404
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,600
you will be the prince of Dan

405
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:32,400
if you go down the mountain now.

406
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:36,360
You are no longer one of us.

407
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:38,240
How about the second?

408
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,760
Secondly, you stay here

409
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:44,760
and you are no longer the prince.

410
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,720
You are just Song of Tianji Peak.

411
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:51,400
We will be with you.

412
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:52,920
And,

413
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:56,880
you should give out the Ruler
and the commander’s seal

414
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:59,120
to prove your determination.

415
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,360
Follow me.

416
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:29,710
Have you decided?

417
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:32,020
I am just Song in Big Dipper

418
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:35,440
from today.

419
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:39,400
Are you here for Chu Min?

420
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:43,280
Yes, and no.

421
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,310
I have grown up in the palace.

422
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:49,000
I’ve seen a lot of intrigue since I was a kid.

423
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,920
Even when I came to Big Dipper,

424
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:53,920
I wanted to take advantage
in the trial of royal clans.

425
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,440
Big Dipper is different.

426
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,800
There is only martial arts here.

427
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,080
It is pure and peace.

428
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:01,480
I am happy here.

429
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,720
So I want to stay

430
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:05,720
and regard you as brother.

431
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:16,240
Chenfeng.

432
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:17,920
Brother.

433
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:19,240
Chenfeng.

434
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,880
You can seal the Thousand Pine Ruler

435
00:35:22,560 --> 00:35:24,920
for your senior Song.

436
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:28,520
Put it in Qisha Institute.

437
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:29,840
Yes. Brother.

438
00:35:31,080 --> 00:35:31,810
Senior Song.

439
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:35,540
It’s a new sword
the brother asked me to make for you.

440
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:38,880
This…

441
00:35:40,640 --> 00:35:41,770
To remote from life.

442
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:43,080
To eliminate ambition.

443
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,480
To stay away from the war.

444
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:48,200
There is one thing you can’t stay away.

445
00:35:49,640 --> 00:35:50,320
Song.

446
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,800
From today,

447
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:55,840
Big Dipper is with you.

448
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:57,760
Since then,

449
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,760
I had made up my mind to forget the past.

450
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:03,450
I only wanted to be the disciple of Big Dipper.

451
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:06,080
But I never thought it wouldn’t be a long time.

452
00:36:06,080 --> 00:36:07,560
I don’t know when

453
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,800
Yan Qiuci found my secret.

454
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,440
He colluded with Zhai Rong.

455
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:12,400
He led them in.

456
00:36:12,760 --> 00:36:14,020
How could that happen?

457
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,540
Uncle Lyu never mentioned that to me.

458
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:19,320
Chenfeng is innocent.

459
00:36:19,720 --> 00:36:20,580
What about you?

460
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:23,120
Have you ever doubted that

461
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,520
why Zhai always hide something from you

462
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,650
but he wants to hire you as an official?

463
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:30,920
He is in the court.

464
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:33,240
Why didn’t he show surprise

465
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:35,480
at your identity of the awakening?

466
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,080
Lu Ping.

467
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,560
Your existence

468
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:48,240
is the plan of him and Yan Qiuci.

469
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,600
Your majesty.

470
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:09,010
Hand out the commander’s seal.

471
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:21,200
Brother.

472
00:37:25,200 --> 00:37:29,080
I heard Master Leng never interfered into politics.

473
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,880
As long as Liu Song hands over
the commander’s seal.

474
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,840
we will not interfere with each other.

475
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,970
Liu Song is the disciple of Big Dipper.

476
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:38,170
He has nothing to do with the court.

477
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:40,080
I am the master of Big Dipper.

478
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:43,120
No one is allowed to make trouble here.

479
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,040
Come on.

480
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:59,900
[Qisha Institute]

481
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,240
Your parents

482
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,160
lost much of their skills

483
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:06,620
in restraining the six forces of you.

484
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:09,450
But they saved me without hesitation.

485
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,840
We went back to Qisha Institute.

486
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:15,120
Your mother saw my injury.

487
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:19,120
She pushed me and you into a secret room.

488
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:23,400
Song.

489
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,330
I will leave Ping’er to you.

490
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,440
Sister.

491
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:28,680
Your brother promised to protect you.

492
00:38:28,680 --> 00:38:30,160
I would fight with him.

493
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:52,760
I didn’t expect that when the door closed,

494
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,260
it would be a farewell.

495
00:38:58,360 --> 00:39:00,320
How miserable they died!

496
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:04,440
Your father was stabbed several times.

497
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:07,440
Your mother was killed by one sword.

498
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,600
For saving us.

499
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:16,840
For us.

500
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:22,440
Yan Qiuci wanted to force me out

501
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:26,120
and burned the Qisha Institute with fire.

502
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:52,420
[Qisha Institute]

503
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:11,760
Brother.

504
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:33,210
I had stayed in the fire for a long time.

505
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,520
I thought about being burned to die

506
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:38,210
with you and your parents in Qisha Institute.

507
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,620
All would be finished.

508
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,760
But brother once said,

509
00:40:44,120 --> 00:40:45,720
there is no value of dying

510
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,720
without saving something.

511
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:50,440
I have to revenge.

512
00:40:49,980 --> 00:40:59,180
[Qisha Institute]

513
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,760
I need to live.

514
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,640
Your majesty. Your majesty.

515
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,360
I am sorry that I come late to rescue.

516
00:41:54,640 --> 00:41:57,080
Do you know why it is called Shanhai Gang?

517
00:41:58,240 --> 00:42:00,360
It is to tell those people

518
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,600
that their sins

519
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:05,400
will not disappear.

